This is very good question it can clear the concept of arrays/vectors and the min and max under the for loop and all.
So the Basic approach is:-
1> Clone that given array/vector to the new array/vector
2> Sort any one of the array/vector
3> initialize the start -> length/size of the nums and end -> 0
4> iterate whole array/vector from i = 0 to i<size then
apply the condition comparing every element of nums and ans
5> Then for the more depth refer to my notes and code Below:-

